Statistical analysis results of baseline (pre-training) measures

Source: R/data.R
BASELINE_STATS.Rd

A data.frame containing statistical analysis results of baseline (pre-training) measures: NMR mass, lean mass, fat mass, mass, maximum run speed.

BASELINE_STATS

Format

An object of class tbl_df (inherits from tbl, data.frame) with 112 rows and 24 columns.

See also

BASELINE_EMM

Examples

unique(BASELINE_STATS$response) # available measures
#> [1] "NMR Weight"        "NMR Lean Mass"     "NMR Fat Mass"     
#> [4] "NMR % Lean"        "NMR % Fat"         "Absolute VO2max"  
#> [7] "Relative VO2max"   "Maximum Run Speed"
